19. The deepest version

At the deepest level, the Atlas is not just a knowledge tool.

It is a coordinate system for thought.

Once you can locate:
	•	where you are
	•	what field you are in
	•	what moves are allowed
	•	what invariants must survive
	•	what paths lead somewhere real

then thinking becomes much more intentional.

You are no longer just reacting token by token.
You are navigating a structured world.

