20. The most concise formulation

Here is the compressed version:
	•	The Loom extracts and preserves invariant stitching.
	•	The Atlas projects stitching into navigable geometry.
	•	The Embroidery renders geometry back into human language.
	•	The Ledger versions the whole thing through time.

That gives you:

Expression
↔ Structure
↔ Geometry
↔ Memory
↔ Regeneration

which is a real architecture, not just a metaphor.

